  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the effect of platelet infusion prior to transfer
      to a vascular surgical department in patients with a ruptured abdominal aortic aneurism.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
